# MarkdownEditor

`TxMarkdownEditor` edits Markdown in three modes: WYSIWYG, source, and preview. It renders Markdown with `marked`, sanitizes HTML through DOMPurify by default, and serializes rich editing content back to Markdown.

## Basic Usage

